# 🍽️ AkuLapar — Food Recommendation Website (PHP-Based)

**AkuLapar** is a web application developed using **PHP**, where users can **register, log in**, and receive **personalized notifications**. The platform aims to help users discover new and trending meals.

This project was built to demonstrate core backend functionality such as **authentication**, **session management**, and **dynamic content rendering** using PHP.

## 🌟 Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication** — Register and log in securely using PHP sessions.
- 📬 **Dynamic Content** — Menu and recommendations are dynamically.
- 📱 **Responsive UI** — Clean layout with responsive design principles.

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **PHP** — Core backend logic
- **MySQL** — Database for storing user credentials and recommendation data
- **HTML/CSS** — Page structure and styling
- **JavaScript** — Frontend interaction
